Diner in Taiwan vomits after biting into cockroach in braised tofu🤮The vendor allegedly offered to waive the fees  but the diner felt they were brushing over the matter.The stall in question is arguably one of the most famous braised pork rice stalls in Keelung City.👉https://tsl.to/cockroachtofu@mustsharenews

The reason that AP Strategic is undergoing this investment deal is to(1) raise additional capital for the proposed acquisition of Mobii Genius (2) Repay a term loan(3) working capitalAll in all  this looks like a strategic placement to a renowned investor  which is eerily similar to Jasper recent deal which saw price propelling from Zero to $0.008.Interesting  it is indeed. I believe it will come alive. But Whether  it will be like Jasper 2.0 or not? If only we know  right?Anyways DYODD  looks a decent gamble  with good RRR at current price.

For those keen to read up on AP Strategic RTO deal on Mobii Genius.Key things to note- Reason for this RTO being  investing in data centres to cater for the worldwide shortage of computing power driven by the increase in ‘AI’ usages- deal is based on new share issuance of $0.00483- Based on their findings  the investment in data centres in SEA is expected to increase to USD $14.19 billion in 2028Source:https://links.sgx.com/1.0.0/corporate-announcements/UJRPDAVY3YCS7VQJ/795071_APSIL%20RTO%20Announcement.pdf
